name: Tree of Life Return Address Stamp - Custom - SELF INKING - DD-007
description:
The Tree of Life return address stamp is made to order. It’s a self inking stamp that can be used on mailing envelopes, invitations or what ever your heart desires. Leave an impression on something with this stamp and let others share your interest with this one of a kind design.

SPECS:
• Stamp impression size is 1 5/8” in diameter.
• Stamp stands at 4.5” tall.
• Available colors are : black, blue , green, red, pink, brown, orange and purple.

HOW TO ORDER:
1. Click the "Add to Cart" button located under the item price.
2. Include the following information for your stamp in the "note to seller" box:
• Name:
• Address:
• City/State:
• Zip:
***A proof will be emailed to you upon request***
3. Select "Pay with Credit Card" or "Pay with PayPal". Once your order is submitted it will be made (unless waiting on proof approval) and shipped within 24 hours of your purchase!
